ooked. Remove Varoma, then remove simmering basket with aid of spatula."},{"content":"Sprinkle spring onions\/shallots over prawns and vermicelli and serve with beans. When serving, mix vermicelli until all are a light brown colour and coated in sauce."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If your shallow bowl is <b>14 cm<b> or larger, ensure the holes of the Varoma dish are not blocked by using a steaming rack, <b>2 small<b> chopsticks or a wooden chopstick broken in two to support the shallow bowl off the bottom of the Varoma dish.<br>- To curl the spring onions, cut into <b>10 cm<b> lengths and then lengthways into thin strips (julienne), place into a bowl of cold water with a few ice cubes and allow to chill approx. <b>20-30 minutes<b> until curled.<br>- If the raw prawns are small <b>(6-7 cm)<b> they can be steamed from frozen."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 15m","4 portions"]}